  <div class="page">
    <p>Conclusion</p>
    <p>Well-implemented 2FA methods may be set up and used without major difficulty</p>
    <p>Home users may not always have access to secondfactor device</p>
    <p>Users differentiate between high and low value accounts</p>
    <p>Time to authenticate decreases with familiarity (U2F, TOTP)</p>
    <p>Faster authentication does not necessarily mean higher usability</p>
